{"tid":2101754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國國務院批准對台軍售方案涉6.2億美元","createTime":"2020-07-10T04:26:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T04:29:34.000Z","uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7ce3d51e8a05daec91e49cd228bb6cf41fbb426c","tid":2101754,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T04:26:18.000Z","msg":"美國國務院正式批准向台灣出售「愛國者三型飛彈」方案，涉及6.2億美元，並知會國會，是繼5月中之後，美國再次通過對台軍售。<br />\n<br />\n軍售方案包括為更換過期組件與認證測試等，美國國務院重申，軍售是基於《台灣關係法》，將令台灣軍隊持續現代化，並保持可靠的防禦能力，符合美國國家、經濟與安全利益，亦有助提高台灣安全，強調軍售不會改變區域基本軍事平衡。台灣軍方對美國的軍售決定表示感謝。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536922-20200710.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536922-20200710.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjlDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=49f6dd0f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536922-20200710.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f22aca4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536922-20200710.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"bd16ea913222c0fe5c8e27c168012f3858887d1f","tid":2101754,"uid":51583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T04:27:05.000Z","msg":"台灣其實自己想買定係硬食"},{"pid":"917189fb59aa494d19a3f9a918ebc9f3fd7fa7be","tid":2101754,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bd16ea913222c0fe5c8e27c168012f3858887d1f","tid":2101754,"uid":51583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T04:27:05.000Z","msg":"台灣其實自己想買定係硬食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T04:28:09.000Z","msg":"當交保護費者"},{"pid":"a718dbb1079da31971ce50fe4639c5b446348b9d","tid":2101754,"uid":64191,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T04:28:22.000Z","msg":"台灣好似本身就有裝吧？"},{"pid":"1c611e64ad972c8a14ce005562bf8beb8461153b","tid":2101754,"uid":323443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0